---
title: Quick Mediterranean Beef Meatballs with Creamy Pesto Dressing & Garden Salad
description: For meatballs with some Mediterranean vibes, lace them with our rich garlic and herb seasoning. Then add an extra layer of flavour by coating them in our caramelised onion chutney before serving over a simple and textural salad to balance out the richness. Don't forget the drizzle of creamy basil pesto dressing to tie everything together.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*

